{"tid":2347431,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"周梓樂死因研訊︱受襲昏迷後再被人掟落樓？ 骨科醫生：冇乜可能","createTime":"2020-12-31T04:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T08:50:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c3e7e3d50f39d3c18da0b37e036fd0c0a4003eef","tid":2347431,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:47:51.000Z","msg":"科大男生周梓樂去年11月4日凌晨於將軍澳警民衝突期間，在尚德邨停車場墮樓昏迷，留醫5天後不治，終年22歲。死因研訊第24天，骨科專科醫生江金富今以專家證人身份作供。他分析梓樂的傷勢、電腦掃瞄、毒理化驗及驗屍等報告後，認為梓樂從高處意外墮下的機會較大，而自行跳下或被人襲擊後掟落樓的機會則較低。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/JU6CJSKVXVFZNFPNXELJXMEDXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FJU6CJSKVXVFZNFPNXELJXMEDXE%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=34688ccc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FJU6CJSKVXVFZNFPNXELJXMEDXE%2F&h=436d516f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/JU6CJSKVXVFZNFPNXELJXMEDXE/</a>"},{"pid":"6913fd141255e5b584d56bdcac9f0a613da5b233","tid":2347431,"uid":4783,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:17:27.000Z","msg":"乜撚野骨科醫生咁撚把炮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2c98e2bcedfd08a493088b3d05e10dbb163aea","tid":2347431,"uid":328494,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認為梓樂從高處意外墮下的機會較大，而自行跳下或被人襲擊後掟落樓的機會則較低。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n&quot;較大&rdquo;，&ldquo;較低&rdquo;即係幾多%？<br />\n51% vs 49%？<br />\n90% vs 10%？<br />\n其他？"},{"pid":"7d52a0ec4008ef3516174e94ec4f55997b1798e4","tid":2347431,"uid":5312,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:29:08.000Z","msg":"等睇叻叻教主入嚟話學Parkour動作失敗"},{"pid":"45d217b3413d1aefde69bbc9d84f7884415dfbb0","tid":2347431,"uid":372210,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"cctoy=專家。"},{"pid":"c0cab2f7f5cfc24cc53c77226db9b1cd1d351633","tid":2347431,"uid":62226,"like":8,"dislike":19,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"7d52a0ec4008ef3516174e94ec4f55997b1798e4","tid":2347431,"uid":5312,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:29:08.000Z","msg":"等睇叻叻教主入嚟話學Parkour動作失敗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:15:32.000Z","msg":"等睇CCtoy 話梓樂俾人扔落樓"},{"pid":"5affc4fc510088be451d4485ba7a6b4ca24ff50b","tid":2347431,"uid":75777,"like":19,"dislike":7,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;例如起跳前看不到矮牆外凌空，左手撐起身體後跨過矮牆，則其眼睛會看著前面、頭部向前衝，最終導致其頭部及右邊身體先著地，致其頭部重創。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n骨科醫生肯撚定冇跨過欄杆<br />\n如果係側身跨欄咁過 <br />\n你會單手推&gt;側身過&gt;腳準備落地<br />\n<br />\n如果你側身過欄後腳唔準備落 肯定會仆街<br />\n有經驗而流暢地做到既 過欄後一定會準備腳<br />\n而且會準備埋仆街時手落地撐住<br />\n<br />\n1. 假設梓樂真係跨欄過<br />\n點解唔係腳/手落地先 而係頭落地先？<br />\n<br />\n2. 佢假設左手撐起過，咁點解會係右邊身體著地先?佢expect 人跨欄會轉身180度?<br />\n<br />\n我真係好想睇下骨科醫生示範一下佢既跨欄大法"},{"pid":"8e410e1eaa667861480f6d875178f90ce428d103","tid":2347431,"uid":138964,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"認為梓樂從高處意外墮下的機會較大，而自行跳下或被人襲擊後掟落樓的機會則較低。<br />\n<br />\n照字面解釋<br />\n即係<br />\n冇意識自行意外墮下<br />\n冇人襲擊後掟落樓<br />\n<br />\n但係有意識墮下又難造出咁既傷勢<br />\n睇黎睇去都唔撚明"},{"pid":"d40c63183ac9e015e19fe591d6ed5d97d1c4df46","tid":2347431,"uid":199771,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6291ad6ae08875d8578c8fcba0b8f159dfb3c7a2","tid":2347431,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6913fd141255e5b584d56bdcac9f0a613da5b233","tid":2347431,"uid":4783,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:17:27.000Z","msg":"乜撚野骨科醫生咁撚把炮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy