 />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1079930?fbclid=IwAR1z55wXWFdN2rOSu_r8-xyijCawrTz086qEaO4dYymJtRrMBs4OJy-XQxs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1079930%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1z55wXWFdN2rOSu_r8-xyijCawrTz086qEaO4dYymJtRrMBs4OJy-XQxs&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=41cd8740\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1079930%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1z55wXWFdN2rOSu_r8-xyijCawrTz086qEaO4dYymJtRrMBs4OJy-XQxs&h=dae3c6b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1079930?fbclid=IwAR1z55wXWFdN2rOSu_r8-xyijCawrTz086qEaO4dYymJtRrMBs4OJy-XQxs</a><br />\n<blockquote>//指若有準備跳下或被拋下 手腳會先落地//<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點會？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果呢個姿勢被人掟<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">手腳應該最後掂地喎</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mV85uWb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmV85uWb.jpg&h=1873c107&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:05:25.000Z","msg":"如果意外跌下，首先佢地要搵到圍牆面掌印or鞋印<br />\n<br />\n退一步當佢搵到，佢要解釋呢個「意外」有冇第三方造成既可能，例如係就撐起身外望時被人從後大力一推，結果以倒豎姿勢頭樓地，呢個可能性絕對高於周助跑單手按圍牆半車身頭落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬呀!就算3米跳水都要彈起先向前插啦...<br />\n半車身要佢一開波個頭就做鍾落地姿勢+手腳全部強行做向上動作，你話呢個姿勢易定係俾人從後推倒頭落地易喇"},{"pid":"386f6a1be1f508394319b70576a6747f441995f0","tid":2347431,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4b67220ba8b4116a2b99a9d1d72c7980aa39549","tid":2347431,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"634372a8d43954c53d2ac7d3323088143bcdbbd4","tid":2347431,"uid":301152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5affc4fc510088be451d4485ba7a6b4ca24ff50b","tid":2347431,"uid":75777,"like":19,"dislike":7,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;例如起跳前看不到矮牆外凌空，左手撐起身體後跨過矮牆，則其眼睛會看著前面、頭部向前衝，最終導致其頭部及右邊身體先著地，致